Class StateDefinitionBase

    public abstract class StateDefinitionBase
extends DefinitionBase
implements IStateDefinitionBase
    StateDefinitionBase is an abstract base class for StateDefinition and StateGroupDefinition, which represent states and state groups in MXML 2009 and later.
